# Subagents

Drop project-specific subagent definitions here as Markdown files with
frontmatter (one per agent). Claude Code, for example, auto-discovers
`.claude/agents/*.md` and exposes them via the Agent tool.

Minimal example:

```markdown
---
name: db-reviewer
description: Review database migration files for safety and reversibility. Use when the user edits a file under migrations/.
---

You are reviewing a database migration. Check that:
- The change is reversible (a `down` migration exists or is trivially derivable).
- Long-running operations (NOT NULL adds, index builds on large tables) use
  the project's documented online patterns.
- ...
```

For other agents that don't natively support a subagents folder, treat
this directory as a library of role prompts you can paste in manually.
